creator: POS Malaysia
descriptionHtml:
Get instant access to Pos Malaysia services now.

Start using our Pos Malaysia mobile app today.

Track your shipping, calculate postage prices, find postcodes and more from your Android or iOS device. Start using our unique app features:

Use Track & Trace to find any delivery or order
For both recipients and senders, you can now use Track & Trace to find any item, or subscribe for notifications to know exactly where it is and when it will arrive.

Use SendParcel Lite
Create single shipments or bulk uploads, and top up your credit with SendParcel Lite.

Get e-Consignment Notes
Ready to start shipping? Create e-consignment notes for your parcels on the go.

Calculate your postage
Check the postage prices for domestic or international mail. Simply select the type of mail you’re sending, enter its weight and we’ll calculate the rest for you.

Search for postcodes
With Postcode Finder, you can find any street address in Malaysia via postcode or location.

Find Pos Malaysia outlets
Whether it’s a post office, an EziBox or a drive-thru counter, you can now locate your nearest Pos Malaysia outlet with ease.

Download the Pos Malaysia app now.

Help us improve our app, products and services with your valuable feedback.

Contact us via:
Email: care@pos.com.my
Website: https://www.efeedback.pos.com.my
Toll-free number: 1-300-300-300

Thank you for choosing Pos Malaysia
